 # Mealshare – Recipe Sharing & Meal Planning App – Project Prompt
Project Goal
To build a mobile-friendly recipe sharing and meal planning app that allows users to share, discover, and plan meals with AI help, focusing on global cuisines, especially African recipes.

Target Users
- Food enthusiasts & home cooks
- Catering schools & students

Main Features
- User registration and login
- Profile creation (user or catering school)
- Recipe posting, liking, saving
- Bulk recipe sharing for catering schools
- TasteBuddy AI recipe suggestions
- Community forum + events
- Follow users
- Recipe collections (for catering schools)
- Notifications for updates

Pages / Layout
- Home Page (Introduction and featured recipes)
- Sign Up / Login Page
- User Dashboard
- Recipe Gallery Page
- Custom Recipe Page
- Community Page
- Profile Settings Page

UI Style Requirements
- Clean and modern food-inspired design
- Soft neutral colors (Primary: Warm Beige, Accents: Fresh Green, Text: Dark Gray)
- Elegant fonts (stylish but readable)
- High-quality food images
- Card-based layout for recipes
- Responsive design (mobile-first approach)
- Simple navigation bar at top or bottom

State Management Needs
- Store logged-in user session
- Save user preferences
- Manage recipe likes, comments
- Store selected recipes temporarily
- Real-time updates for recipe progress

Authentication Needs
- Users must sign up and log in
- Email and password authentication
- Role-based access (User or Catering School)
- Password reset option
- Secure data storage

Design Constraints
- Must be mobile-friendly
- Must load quickly
- Simple and easy-to-use interface
- Secure user data protection
- Follow modern UI/UX best practices
- Must work properly on both Android and iPhone browsers

Tagline
_sharing meals, building a community_
